---
title: Beyond Meat® and Spinach Rigatoni with Chili Flakes
description: Beyond Meat® is spiced with Italian seasonings and chili flakes for a delicious sausage fake-out! Spinach and crushed tomatoes get tossed with cream to create a beautiful, blushing sauce. Don't forget about the perfectly al dente rigatoni pasta!
